rows.label: tlk41300022_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Gula's such a peaceful place.
Never seen it any other way.

rows.label: tlk41300022_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm with the Militia Corps, but we've so
much free time on our hands, we don't
know what to do with ourselves.

rows.label: tlk41300022_01_msg0003
rows.name:
What with us and the Superbian army
stationed here, no one dares start
making any trouble.

rows.label: tlk41300022_01_msg0004
rows.name:
There was a tiny little incident a short
while back, but I don't suppose much
came of it.
